const headHtml = "<title>New Fishing Island Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"An expert based guide to Hypixel SkyBlock's new fishing island system, covering the outpost revamp, bites, boat upgrades, early merchant changes and how this foundation carries into patch 0.25 Lotus Atoll.\">\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/new-fishing-island-guide-2026\">\n\n    <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/new-fishing-island-guide-2026\">\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\">\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"New Fishing Island Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock\">\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"The new fishing island update is really an outpost, boat and stat-system update, so learn the infrastructure first and the island loop gets much easier.\">\n    <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/static/NEC.png\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"New Fishing Island Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock\",\"description\":\"Expert based guide to Hypixel SkyBlock's new fishing island system.\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-22\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-06-22\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"NotEnoughCoins\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Coflnet GmbH\"},\"url\":\"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/new-fishing-island-guide-2026\"}</script>";
const bodyHtml = "<main><div class=\"site-shell article-layout\"><article class=\"article\"><a class=\"article-meta\" href=\"/guides#months-list\">Scheduled 2026-06-22 • Fishing Update (see 0.25 follow-up)</a><h1>New Fishing Island Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock</h1><p class=\"lede\">The new fishing island update is bigger than one destination. It rebuilds the fishing outpost, introduces a boat progression system, adds bites and stat explanations, refreshes the merchant flow and starts hinting at a larger fishing map that Hypixel can expand over time. If you approach it as just another island unlock, you miss the real value. The update is teaching players a new fishing infrastructure. For the full Lotus Atoll launch follow-up, continue with the <a href=\"/guides/hypixel-skyblock-0-25-lotus-atoll-update\">Hypixel SkyBlock 0.25 Lotus Atoll Update Guide</a>.</p><div class=\"note\"><strong>Primary source base:</strong> creator coverage of the revamped fishing outpost and first special island, paired with official 0.24.3 notes on Jerry fishing changes and hotspots. The goal here is to separate stable systems from early patch excitement.</div><h2>Start with the outpost, not the island hype</h2><p>The first useful change is the path into fishing. The new objective flow walks players from the main island to a lake NPC, gives them a starter rod and then pushes them into the rebuilt fishing outpost. That outpost is the real update hub. It is larger, easier to understand and packed with NPCs that explain bites, stats, merchants and later progression. For returning players, this is the cleanest way Hypixel has ever explained why fishing speed, sea creature chance, treasure chance and double hook matter.</p><p>Bites are especially important because they turn fishing buffs into a visible decision instead of hidden trivia. Some improve fishing speed, others help with specific mob or treasure outcomes. That makes the new outpost more than a visual revamp. It is a tutorial zone for the modern fishing stat stack.</p><h2>The boat system is the long-term progression</h2><p>The headline mechanic is your personal boat. The boat has three upgradeable parts: helm, engine and hull. Early creator coverage showed bronze upgrades adding fishing wisdom and implied that stronger versions will gate later islands. Right now the public focus is on the first island, but the smarter read is that Hypixel is building a framework for several fishing destinations, not a one-off travel gimmick.</p><p>That matters for planning. If you want to be ready for future fishing content or Guardian Slayer follow-ups, invest in the account-level fishing engine first. Unlock the outpost, learn the boat flow and price the required mats before you start guessing which island drop will be the next jackpot.</p><h2>Merchant changes matter for money routes too</h2><p>The updated fishing merchant and the new accessory branches are not just tutorial clutter. They directly affect how fast early fishing setups become usable. Creator coverage highlighted Angler Armor as the first practical armor step and pointed out that the accessory line splits into defensive and offensive versions against sea creatures. Combined with new stats like treasure chance, that means the fishing economy will not only revolve around raw fish prices. It will also revolve around progression parts, upgrade mats and whatever future islands ask from your boat.</p><p>Use <a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/bazaar\">SkyCofl bazaar</a> to watch fast-moving fishing mats, <a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/topMovers\">SkyCofl top movers</a> for sudden spikes, <a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/demand\">BazaarTracker demand</a> to confirm the items actually sell and <a href=\"https://pro.skyblock.bz/features/market-trends\">BazaarPro market trends</a> when you want a broader picture of whether the move has already started cooling off.</p><h2>Read next</h2><ul class=\"related-list\"><li><a href=\"/guides/hypixel-skyblock-0-25-lotus-atoll-update\">Hypixel SkyBlock 0.25 Lotus Atoll Update Guide</a></li><li><a href=\"/guides/post-lotus-atoll-economy-recap\">Post-Lotus Atoll Economy Recap: What Settled and What Didn't</a></li><li><a href=\"/guides/guardian-slayer-guide-2026\">Guardian Slayer Update Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock</a></li><li><a href=\"/guides/new-hub-guide-2026\">New Hub Guide for Hypixel SkyBlock</a></li></ul></article><aside class=\"article-aside\"><div><h3>Best paired tools</h3><ul class=\"tool-list\"><li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/bazaar\">SkyCofl bazaar</a></li><li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/topMovers\">SkyCofl top movers</a></li><li><a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/demand\">BazaarTracker demand</a></li><li><a href=\"https://pro.skyblock.bz/features/market-trends\">BazaarPro market trends</a></li><li><a href=\"https://skyblock.bz/manipulate\">Skyblock.bz manipulation</a></li><li><a href=\"https://skyblock.bz/crash\">Skyblock.bz crash risk</a></li></ul></div><div><h3>Best for</h3><p>Returning fishing players who want to understand the new progression stack before future islands and slayer content raise the skill floor.</p></div><div><h3>Source videos</h3><p>Built from a creator overview of the new fishing outpost, boat parts, merchant changes and the first special island, then cross-checked against the official 0.24.3 fishing notes.</p></div></aside></div></main>";
